  <brief_title>Treatment of Lung Adenocarcinoma With Bronchioloalveolar Feature</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II of Gefitinib (IRESSA) Administered as First-line Treatment in Patients With Non-resectable Pneumonic-type Adenocarcinoma (P-ADC)</official_title>
